1.4. "Display" means to make the Covered Software available on a computer
screen or similar display device.

1.5. "Distribution" means the act of either Making Available or Exporting the
Covered Software, or a combination of both.

1.6. "Executable" means Covered Software in any form other than Source Code.

1.7. "Export" means to send or take the Covered Software out of the jurisdiction
in which it is originally made available for Distribution.

1.8. "Incompatible With Secondary Licenses" means either that the initial
Contributor has attached the notice described in Exhibit B to the Covered
