the notice described in Exhibit C to the Covered Software.

1.9. "Larger Work" means a work that combines Covered Software with other
material, in one or more files, that is not Covered Software.

1.10. "Making Available" means to make the Covered Software available on a
computer network or otherwise for remote access by others, or to distribute the
Covered Software on a computer network or otherwise for remote download by
others.

1.11. "Modifications" means any of the following:

    (a) any file in Source Code form that results from an addition to,
