1.13. "Source Code" means the Covered Software in the form in which it is
usually distributed, including all accompanying documentation.

1.14. "You" or "Your" means an individual or a legal entity exercising rights
under this License. For legal entities, "You" or "Your" includes any entity
that controls, is controlled by, or is under common control with, You. For
